Package com.twiceagain.selescript

Class SSConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.twiceagain.selescript.SSConfig
  • public class SSConfig
extends java.lang.Object
    Configuration information and related utilities. These information are supposed to remain fixed when the program is running. Live informations can be found in the RuntimeContext object.
